Class QueryResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.explorviz.shared.querying.QueryResult<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the objects returned

    public final class QueryResult<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Result of a performed Query by a Queryable. Contains the actual results and additional metadata.
